channel.title: [Release] The new god Nuthesian's Armor and weapons [Release]
channel.description:
Re-releasing cause my old post was deleted :) Download the models here and read the readme: [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/file/mmogyquu2le/Release.zip]http://www.mediafire.com/file/mmogyquu2le/Release.zip[/URL] Thanks guys for all the feedback!!! [size=24pt]THE MELEE IS COMPLETELY CUSTOM BUT THE MAGE AND RANGE ARE PARTIALLY RECOLORS[/size] [COLOR=Orange] P.S. Feel free to make Nuthesian god related stuff if you want. Please post any new armor, weapons, npc, or anything you make here and ill give you my feedback!!![/COLOR]
I like it but stop using the current gods, Someone should be creative and make an all new god with its own mini game and design, That would impress a heck of alot of people.
For the past week or so I've been working on creating a new god. I will update all the information on it here and all the models will be shown here. Please tell me if I should release or not! P.S. Thank you Vice!!! Enjoy... Full with godsword [IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq15/Owner_Fritz/The%20god%20Nuthesian/ConseptwithGodsword.png[/img] Full with scim and shield [IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq15/Owner_Fritz/The%20god%20Nuthesian/ConseptwithSkimandShield.png[/img] Full with warspear [IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq15/Owner_Fritz/The%20god%20Nuthesian/Conseptwithspear.png[/img] (original spear was Cj's before I edited) Here's ur credits Mr. Linksys P.S. i made it the right size so it fits you...not like how yours drags in the dirt Range Full with Longbow [IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq15/Owner_Fritz/The%20god%20Nuthesian/Conseptwithlongbow.png[/img] Range Full with C'bow [IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq15/Owner_Fritz/The%20god%20Nuthesian/Conseptwithcbow.png[/img] Full Mage with Battlestaff [IMG]http://i429.photobucket.com/albums/qq15/Owner_Fritz/The%20god%20Nuthesian/Conseptwithstaff.png[/img]
